<html>
  <head>
    <title>Portal System - EXPO'25</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, user-scalable=no"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/main.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="is-preload">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header id="header">
      <div class="inner">
        <a href="#" class="image avatar"
          ><img src="images/logo.jpg" alt=""
        /></a>
        <h1>
          <strong>I am Project 1164!</strong>, a super simple Portal System<br />
          crafted for STI Marikina's SHS Expo '25!
        </h1>
      </div>
    </header>
    <!-- Menu Toggle -->
    <a
      href="#menu"
      class="menuToggle"
      style="background-color: black; border-radius: 20%; font-size: 1.2em"
      ><span>Menu</span></a
    >
    <!-- Menu -->
    <nav id="menu">
      <a href="#" class="close"><span>Close</span></a>
      <h2>Menu</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/arts">Arts</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main -->
    <div id="main">
      <!-- One -->
      <section id="one">
        <header class="major">
          <h2>
            Welcome to the Portal System of<br />
            STI Marikina's SHS Expo '25!
          </h2>
        </header>
        <p>
          So I start a revolution from my bed 'Cause you said the brains I had
          went to my head Step outside, summertime's in bloom Stand up beside
          the fireplace Take that look from off your face You ain't ever gonna
          burn my heart out And so, Sally can wait She knows it's too late as
          we're walkin' on by Her soul slides away "But don't look back in
          anger," I heard you say
        </p>
        <ul class="actions">
          <li><a href="/arts" class="button">Learn More</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Two -->
      <section id="two">
        <h2 style="font-size: 2em">Recent Arts</h2>
        <div class="row">
          {%- for post in collections.post -%}
          <article class="col-6 col-12-xsmall work-item">
            <a href="{{ post.data.product_image }}" class="image fit thumb"
              ><img
                src="{{ post.data.product_image }}"
                alt=""
                style="
                  aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
                  object-fit: cover;
                  width: 100%;
                  height: auto;
                "
              />
            </a>

            <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: bold">
              <a href="/arts#{{ post.data.identifier }}">
                {{ post.data.product_name }}
              </a>
            </h3>

            <p style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: bold">
              {{ post.data.product_section }}
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem">
              {{ post.data.product_description }}
              <a href="/arts#{{ post.data.identifier }}">Learn More</a>
            </p>
          </article>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer id="footer">
      <div class="inner">
        <ul class="icons">
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon brands fa-twitter"
              ><span class="label">Twitter</span></a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon brands fa-github"
              ><span class="label">Github</span></a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon brands fa-dribbble"
              ><span class="label">Dribbble</span></a
            >
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="#" class="icon solid fa-envelope"
              ><span class="label">Email</span></a
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="copyright">
          <li>&copy; Portal System Team</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="assets/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/jquery.poptrox.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/browser.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/breakpoints.min.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/util.js"></script>
    <script src="assets/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
